## 📋 Setup Checklist

### Before Uploading to GitHub

- [ ] Review all markdown files for accuracy
- [ ] Test all commands mentioned
- [ ] Check all links work
- [ ] Verify no sensitive data included
- [ ] Add your GitHub username to references
